
Case 1 - Successful login (happy flow)

1. Perform verification of Auth screen.
    a.Authorization form title is displayed.
    b.Restore password link is displayed.
    c.Register link is displayed.
2. Fill in valid login <Student>.
3. Fill in valid password <909090>.
4. Click submit - "Вход" button.
5. Perform verification of Main Page.
    a. Main page title logo is displayed.
    b. Sidebar toggle button is displayed.
    c. Footer copyright link is displayed.
*6. Perform logout


Case 2 - Unsuccessful login (negative)

1. Perform verification of Sign In screen.
    a.Authorization form title is displayed.
    b.Restore password link is displayed.
    c.Register link is displayed.
2. Fill in invalid login <Student123>.
3. Fill in valid password <909090>.
4. Check if Password textinput is cleared -- "Password" tip is displayed.
5. Fill in valid login <Student>.
6. Fill in invalid password <1234567>.
7. Check if Password textinput is cleared -- "Password" tip is displayed.

Case 3 - Add apparatus "Аппарат"

Precondition - User is already logged in.

1. Click Dictionaries - "Словари" on sidebar.
2. Click Apparatus - "Аппарат" in opened drop-down.
3. Perform verification of Apparatus list page
    a. Apparatus list page main title is displayed.
    b. Apparatus list page box title is displayed.
4. Click Add apparatus button.
5. Fill in apparatus number <2362>.
6. Fill in apparatus comment <Fuel flow controller>.
7. Click Create -- "Создать" button.
8. Scroll to the bottom of the list.
9. Check if apparatus record is created.
10. Click on apparatus record.
11. Remove apparatus.
12. Scroll to the bottom of the list.
13. Check if apparatus record is removed.
*14. Perform logout
